ComicInfo.Summary: Titans Hunt, Chapter Seven: Swan Song: Lilith reveals that she hired the villains from Diablo -- who are now attacking them -- to help them against Mister Twister, but that they must be turning against the Titans because they believe Twister will use the heroes as his pawns. Meanwhile, Garth, Donna Troy, and Nightwing find Mal Duncan at the top of the tower, along with Mister Twister himself.
